==以最冷著名的區域或物體==
*[[回力棒星雲|回力棒星雲]]是[[宇宙|宇宙]]中已知溫度最冷的區域，溫度估計為热力学温标1 K（攝氏-272.15 °C）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/releases/97/coldspot.html|title=Boomerang Nebula boasts the coolest spot in the Universe|date=June 20, 1997|publisher=NASA's Jet Propulsion Laboratory|accessdate=July 8, 2009|archive-date=2009-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827115717/http://jpl.nasa.gov/news/releases/97/coldspot.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*在地球[[利薩如軌道|利薩如軌道]]上的[[赫雪爾太空望遠鏡|赫雪爾太空望遠鏡]]用大量的氦冷卻，使儀器維持在2 K<ref>{{cite news | author=Jonathan Amos | title='Silver Sensation' Seeks Cold Cosmos | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7864087.stm | work=BBC News | date=9 February 2009 | accessdate=2009-03-06 | archive-date=2017-12-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228082718/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7864087.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*[[宇宙背景輻射|宇宙背景輻射]]大約是對應溫度2.725 K的[[黑體輻射|黑體輻射]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Hinshaw | first = Gary | date = December 15, 2005 | url = http://map.gsfc.nasa.gov/m_uni/uni_101bbtest3.html | title = Tests of the Big Bang: The CMB | publisher = NASA WMAP | accessdate = 2007-01-09 | archive-date = 2007-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070110082908/http://map.gsfc.nasa.gov/m_uni/uni_101bbtest3.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
*[[海王星|海王星]]的衛星[[海衛一|海衛一]]表面溫度為−235 °C。
*[[天王星|天王星]]的大氣溫度為−215 °C<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/uranus_worldbook.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-10-06 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60qT840qC?url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/uranus_worldbook.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*[[土星|土星]]最冷的溫度為−175 °C (−285 °F)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/saturn_worldbook.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/616W1CQJQ?url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/saturn_worldbook.html |archivedate=2011-08-21 }}</ref>。
*[[水星|水星]]雖離太陽最近，但因為沒有大氣層可以儲存來自太陽的能量底，背對太陽的一側溫度很低，約有−170 °C<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/mercury_worldbook.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-09-26 |archive-date=2010-01-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5mq2ainKL?url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/mercury_worldbook.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*[[木星|木星]]最冷的溫度為−145 °C (−230 °F)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/jupiter_worldbook.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-08-10 |archive-date=2005-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050105155019/http://www.nasa.gov/worldbook/jupiter_worldbook.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
